<BaseLayout
  title="Our Services | EES"
  description="Energy-efficient solutions for homes and businesses — solar, batteries, hydronic comfort conditioning, heat pumps, and smart automation."
>
  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Our Services</h1>
      <p>Energy-efficient solutions for homes and businesses.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container prose">
      <h2>Residential</h2>
      <p>
        We design and install complete energy systems for homes — from solar panels and batteries to hydronic heating/cooling and smart automation.
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong><a href="/services/residential/solar-systems">Solar Systems</a></strong> — rooftop PV designed for your energy profile</li>
        <li><strong><a href="/services/residential/battery-systems">Battery Systems</a></strong> — store solar energy for use day and night</li>
        <li><strong><a href="/services/residential/comfort-conditioning">Comfort Conditioning</a></strong> — radiant hydronic ceiling panels for heating and cooling</li>
        <li><strong><a href="/services/residential/heat-pump-systems">Heat Pump Systems</a></strong> — polyvalent heat pumps for heating, cooling, and hot water</li>
        <li><strong><a href="/services/residential/home-automation">Home Automation</a></strong> — intelligent control of your energy and comfort systems</li>
        <li><strong><a href="/services/residential/virtual-power-plants">Virtual Power Plants (VPPs)</a></strong> — earn from your battery by sharing stored solar energy</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Commercial</h2>
      <p>
        Commercial solar and battery systems, scaled for business.
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong><a href="/services/commercial/solar-systems">Solar Systems</a></strong> — rooftop and ground-mount for commercial buildings</li>
        <li><strong><a href="/services/commercial/battery-systems">Battery Systems</a></strong> — peak demand reduction and backup power</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Consultation &amp; Support</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong><a href="/services/consultation">Free Consultation</a></strong> — we assess your property and design a system tailored to your needs</li>
        <li><strong><a href="/services/financing">Financing Options</a></strong> — flexible payment options to make the switch affordable</li>
        <li><strong><a href="/services/faq">FAQs</a></strong> — common questions about our systems and process</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
